name: Adithya Ganesh
text: Tasty pizzas. They have a wonderful mini pizza option for quick bites with less price... they have veggies option too..

name: Nickolas Benesh
text: Good pizza for good price. As of 1/12/18 every other Friday they either have $1 slices or $5 mini-pizzas plus 22oz drink.
